{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"1fa62b0ff8","title":"同意先打黄维","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"8d922686b4","index":0,"year":1948,"month":11,"day":24,"articleId":"1fa62b0ff8"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji25","name":"毛泽东全集第25卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji25.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji25":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"a51d762460","type":"paragraph","text":"同意先打黄维口","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji25","articleId":"1fa62b0ff8"},{"id":"74c1c48674","type":"paragraph","text":"（1948年11月24日）刘、陈、邓，并香菜、陈、张”模二十二时电”悉。（一）完全同意先打黄维”：（二）望菜陈张遵刘陈邓部署，派必要兵力参加打黄维：（三）情况紧急时机，一切由刘陈邓临机处置，不要请示","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji25","articleId":"1fa62b0ff8"},{"id":"8deba716b7","type":"paragraph","text":"军委","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji25","articleId":"1fa62b0ff8"},{"id":"3e2c4ca7ce","type":"paragraph","text":"二十四日十五时[1]这是毛泽东为中共中央军委起草的给中原野战年司令员刘伯承、第[2]果、陈、张，指果裕、陈士架、张震，当时分别任华东野战军代司令民美代致治受员、参谋长和参谋长。[3]指1948年11月23日22时刘伯承、陈毅、邓小平关于先牙黄维兵团的都署婚菜帮、陈士燥、张震开报中共中央军委的电报。电报说：现齐击们即原北实行。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji25","articleId":"1fa62b0ff8"}],"page":{"id":"3554284d05","publicationId":"maoquanji25","articleId":"1fa62b0ff8","start":268,"end":268}}}},"__N_SSG":true}